<aotw-stepper>
  <aotw-step
    *ngFor="let step of steps; let i = index"
    [active]="activeStep === i"
    [disabled]="step.disabled"
    (click)="setActiveStep(i)"
  >

  </aotw-step>
</aotw-stepper>
